item.title: My First Blog Post
item.description:
First Blog Post

by comedicomedy. 8/3/24 - 7:30 pm

introduction

Hi I'm comedicomedy. I'm an aspiring enginner who also has an interest in music. I made this website to by my space on the internet. After watching videos on the personal web by psychcool and You've Got Kat I was inspired to make my own site. I want to share random things I'm interested in every week. I'll probably make blogs about things related to stem and computer science.
